response.overview: On her debut stand up special, Not Smart Enough, recorded at The Gutter in Brooklyn, Janet McNamara discusses workplace annoyances, why sex is stupid, and how various health professionals have suggested she get tested for autism. Janet is a Boston native who Maria Bamford calls “a fantastic comic with an amazing delivery and enviable timing of very unique material.” Janet’s singular perspective and unpretentious delivery will leave you laughing...and questioning societal norms.
response.title: Janet McNamara: Not Smart Enough
